A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Child Care Centers – Certificated Staff Ratio Requirement – Repeal
3 FOR the purpose of repealing a requirement that certain child care centers have in
4 attendance a certain ratio of staff to children who hold a certificate in first aid and
5 cardiopulmonary resuscitation under certain circumstances; and generally relating
6 to child care centers and staffing requirements.
